      <title>Pope Leo returns 62 artifacts to Indigenous peoples from Canada</title>
      <author>The Associated Press</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/11/15/nx-s1-5609835/vatican-pope-returns-indigenous-artifacts-canada</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/11/15/nx-s1-5609835/vatican-pope-returns-indigenous-artifacts-canada</comments>
